| 
| Extract designed for synchronisation of Contributions between openEHR servers.
| 

class SYNC_EXTRACT
    is_a MESSAGE_CONTENT

feature_group ("access")

    | 
    | Details of specification of this Extract.
    | 
    prop specification: SYNC_EXTRACT_SPEC;

    | 
    | Content, in the form of a serialised Contributions.
    | 
    prop items: List<X_CONTRIBUTION>;


end
